*fping-2.4_beta2-r2 (24 Oct 2008)

  24 Oct 2008; Peter Volkov <pva@gentoo.org> +fping-2.4_beta2-r2.ebuild:
  Added suid bin on fping binary, required by many monitoring tools
  (nagious, zabbix), bug #241930, thank Rolf Wathne and Dawid Węgliński
  for report.

  06 Sep 2007; Markus Ullmann <jokey@gentoo.org> -fping-2.4_beta2.ebuild:
  Cleanup

  20 Feb 2007; Markus Ullmann <jokey@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Redigest for Manifest2

  20 Jul 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  fping-2.4_beta2-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword as per bug #141142.

  05 Mar 2006; Markus Ullmann <jokey@gentoo.org> fping-2.4_beta2.ebuild,
  fping-2.4_beta2-r1.ebuild:
  COPYING cleanup

  05 Aug 2004; Alexander Plank <alexander@gentoo.org> fping-2.4_beta2.ebuild:
  add macos keyword
  31 Jul 2004; Tom Gall <tgall@gentoo.org> fping-2.4_beta2-r1.ebuild:
  stable on ppc64, bug #57454

  09 Jul 2004; Eldad Zack <eldad@gentoo.org> fping-2.4_beta2-r1.ebuild:
  added missing IUSE

  17 Feb 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> fping-2.4_beta2-r1.ebuild:
  stable on alpha and ia64

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
